      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "7a610b0e723d45ba",
      "text": "Cognitive brain networks such as the default-mode network, frontoparietal network, and salience network, are key functional networks of the human brain. Here we show that the rapid evolutionary cortical expansion of cognitive networks in the human brain, and most pronounced the default-mode network, runs parallel with high expression of human-accelerated genes. [https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-019-12764-8 nature]"
    },
